channel.title: YourClient V1! Added Pictures and Videos!
channel.description:
Hello and welcome to my first client/server download! Uhmm Ive worked on this server for a pretty long time with the help of my friend Josh(Skype). I finally just decided to stop this project and start another one so I'm putting this server up for download!
[b][u]Features:[/u][/b] *Godwars! *Kbd! *A Gnome Glider that you can actually travel by! *Team and Solo Pking. *Donator Shop with actual and good models! For the rest of the features download and see!
[b]Skills:[/b] *All skills work that I know of. Check for yourself when you download I don't have much time to.
[b]Areas:[/b] [color=maroon]Skilling Area - 5% done I was re-doing. Abyss Rcing - 100% Shops - 100% With good models. Donator Zone - 100% shop with great model and correct models. Training Zones - 100% [/color]
[b]NOTE!![/b] Barrows was not done at all when I got this server Skype and I well Skype worked hard to help me get a somewhat working Barrows. I'm not sure if there is a barrows teleport so you have to check! When you download there is 3 errors the need fixed. You can still login but sometimes you get kicked.
[b][u]BUGS:[/u][/b] [b]*There is 1 major bug that I know of! and its when you die you don't spawn anywhere! When I post pictures ill post a video to explain what I mean.[/b] [b]Video![/b] [URL=http://tinypic.com/m/6j3gbo/3]View My Video[/URL] [URL=http://tinypic.com/m/6j3giw/3]View My Video[/URL]
These are the errors:
[code]clickingMost.java:297: 'else' without 'if' } else { ^ clickingMost.java:565: orphaned case case 75001: ^ clickingMost.java:3077: class, interface, or enum expected }→ ^ 3 errors[/code]
One last thing i forgot to mention about barrows is if you download you need to work on it!!
[b]Pictures:[/b] [IMG]http://i45.tinypic.com/okc4uq.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i49.tinypic.com/abmlbk.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i45.tinypic.com/do3xp0.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i47.tinypic.com/72bsif.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i47.tinypic.com/2zh4idj.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i46.tinypic.com/mrvc46.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i50.tinypic.com/2im6vjb.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i50.tinypic.com/2rz5pqt.jpg[/img]
[b]Vidoes:[/b] [URL=http://tinypic.com/m/6j3go5/3]View My Video[/URL] [URL=http://tinypic.com/m/6j3gpt/3]View My Video[/URL]
[b]Credits[/b] Me - 5% for editing The Guy I got source from - 45% for source Skype - 50% for making a base for Barrows/Server editing Also wanna say thanks for everyone who helped!
The Client and Server are all in the folder just open and you will see each folder.
Download Link: [url=http://www.MegaShare.com/1657437]http://www.MegaShare.com/1657437[/url]
Please Enjoy And Comment and Rep? Please don't flame if you don't like.
